trans-unit.source: Represents an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.UserControl"></xref> class that is specified for output caching and included declaratively in a page or another user control.
trans-unit.target: 表示的实例<xref href="System.Web.UI.UserControl"></xref>类，是为输出缓存指定并以声明方式包含在一个页面或另一个用户控件。

trans-unit.source: An instance of this class is created when a user control is specified for output caching, using either an directive in the declarative .ascx file, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.PartialCachingAttribute> class in the user control's code-behind file.
trans-unit.target: 用户控件指定为输出缓存，在声明性.ascx 文件中，使用任一指令时创建此类的实例或<xref:System.Web.UI.PartialCachingAttribute>用户控件的代码隐藏文件中的类。</xref:System.Web.UI.PartialCachingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: When the user control is included declaratively in its containing page (as opposed to being dynamically loaded using the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl.LoadControl%2A> method in the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl> control class), the StaticPartialCachingControl instance is placed in the control hierarchy of the page as a parent to the cached user control.
trans-unit.target: 当用户控件以声明方式包括在其包含的页 (而不是动态正在加载使用<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl.LoadControl%2A>中的方法<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl>控件类)，StaticPartialCachingControl 实例放置在控件层次结构中的页面以作为缓存的用户控件的父级。</xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateControl.LoadControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StaticPartialCachingControl"></xref> object to contain the cached server control content.
trans-unit.target: 创建<xref href="System.Web.UI.StaticPartialCachingControl"></xref>对象，以包含缓存的服务器控件内容。

trans-unit.source: The StaticPartialCachingControl constructor is intended for use by the ASP.NET page framework and should not be called directly by developers.
trans-unit.target: StaticPartialCachingControl 构造函数旨在用于由 ASP.NET 页面框架，不应由开发人员的直接调用。

trans-unit.target: 从服务器控件传递的全局唯一标识符。
